179895.name: Share of global annual CO2 emissions from coal
179895.description: Annual production-based emissions of carbon dioxide (CO2) from coal, measured as a percentage of global production-based emissions of CO2 from coal in the same year. This is based on territorial emissions, which do not account for emissions embedded in traded goods. Each country's share of global CO2 emissions from coal has been calculated by Our World in Data using global CO2 emissions from coal provided in the Global Carbon Budget dataset. Global coal emissions include all country emissions.
